CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 30, 1953, pg. 23, reads: "Muscle Men - Alex Pilin, Richard Madden and Bob Solomon, left to right, were participants in Mr. Western Pennsylvania contest held at Knoxville Junior High School last week. Madden came through with an award for having the nearest to perfect legs in contest. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three bodybuilders, #3 Alex Pilin, #8 Richard Madden, and #16 Bob Solomon, posed in Knoxville Junior High School for Mr. Western Pennsylvania contest
